1
00:00:01,010 --> 00:00:07,409
I bow to all the seekers of truth.

2
00:00:07,489 --> 00:00:18,520
As I told you before, that the Spirit has the nature of being the truth itself,

3
00:00:20,450 --> 00:00:23,670
and this truth is the love of God.

4
00:00:25,860 --> 00:00:37,119
So the truth is, that God is love, that this power that works in you is love.

5
00:00:41,369 --> 00:00:47,899
Love of God, and love of God is pure love.

6
00:00:49,717 --> 00:00:55,489
We have lost the sense of purity because of our own venturesomeness,

7
00:00:55,569 --> 00:01:00,930
but purity is where the love has no lust, no greed.

8
00:01:01,419 --> 00:01:02,619
It is innocent.

9
00:01:06,230 --> 00:01:09,150
Like the sap in the tree rises,

10
00:01:10,360 --> 00:01:15,724
nourishes the whole tree and goes back; it does not get attached to any

11
00:01:15,804 --> 00:01:21,224
particular flower or to any particular leaf and says that,

12
00:01:21,304 --> 00:01:25,860
“I like this.” It is absolutely detached.

13
00:01:25,947 --> 00:01:32,809
It just nourishes and goes back, but carnal love is like the sap rises,

14
00:01:32,889 --> 00:01:42,099
goes into a flower and gets lost; thus the flower will also die, the tree will

15
00:01:45,043 --> 00:01:55,670
also die, and one must understand that when you get after Realization,

16
00:01:55,750 --> 00:02:07,569
what you have to do is first of all to see yourself, how much you love others.

17
00:02:10,610 --> 00:02:16,860
How much your heart has opened for love.

18
00:02:16,940 --> 00:02:19,569
How much you can share.

19
00:02:19,649 --> 00:02:22,539
The individualism should drop out.

20
00:02:23,329 --> 00:02:25,529
That is collective consciousness.

21
00:02:26,960 --> 00:02:32,240
It does not mean that you can feel the chakras of another person.

22
00:02:32,369 --> 00:02:35,899
You can feel the chakras that you have the problems.

23
00:02:35,979 --> 00:02:38,970
You go on like that.

24
00:02:39,050 --> 00:02:44,690
It means that when the Spirit starts shining in your attention,

25
00:02:44,820 --> 00:02:52,610
first thing that you develop a great compassion for this human race.

26
00:02:53,270 --> 00:02:58,470
Not for the animals or for the bugs like the many vegetarians do,

27
00:02:58,550 --> 00:03:00,720
but for the human beings.

28
00:03:00,800 --> 00:03:03,440
They are the epitome of evolution.

29
00:03:06,110 --> 00:03:11,911
So you develop your love for other human beings

30
00:03:11,991 --> 00:03:14,850
because they become part and parcel of your being.

31
00:03:14,930 --> 00:03:22,360
Now for example, a finger is sick and the other finger looks after it.

32
00:03:22,440 --> 00:03:31,079
It is not doing any obligation, but actually it is soothing because

33
00:03:31,159 --> 00:03:38,830
if this is soothed, all the body comes to a very pleasant state.

34
00:03:38,910 --> 00:03:45,759
If this is unpleasant, the whole body is in an unpleasant state.

35
00:03:46,774 --> 00:03:52,069
So if you treat one finger, you are treating the whole.

36
00:03:52,149 --> 00:04:00,163
In the same way, your compassion starts flowing, but many people have very funny

37
00:04:00,243 --> 00:04:06,720
ideas about compassion also and these must be corrected through experimentation.

38
00:04:08,889 --> 00:04:14,139
Some of the ideas of compassion are that you should worry all

39
00:04:14,219 --> 00:04:18,700
the time about people who are absolutely at the low ebb of life.

40
00:04:19,957 --> 00:04:23,890
As a Mother I would say, you have to first mature yourself.

41
00:04:25,479 --> 00:04:29,679
As children you are still growing, that is what humility means.

42
00:04:30,396 --> 00:04:34,929
Understand that you have to still become the Spirit in the full way,

43
00:04:35,380 --> 00:04:39,686
and just now to jump to tasks of taking

44
00:04:39,766 --> 00:04:43,970
up very difficult cases will be very dangerous and you

45
00:04:44,050 --> 00:04:48,900
may get enwrapped into it and your progress may stop.

46
00:04:48,980 --> 00:04:52,187
So as humble students of Sahaja Yoga,

47
00:04:53,220 --> 00:05:01,713
first you have to learn how to master it yourself, to become

48
00:05:01,793 --> 00:05:07,759
a person who does not catch from other people,

49
00:05:07,839 --> 00:05:11,329
who does not get troubles from other people.

50
00:05:11,519 --> 00:05:16,049
In a way, such a person has to be very cautious.

51
00:05:18,760 --> 00:05:21,149
Now I have seen so many people.

52
00:05:23,496 --> 00:05:25,229
They come to the programs,

53
00:05:25,309 --> 00:05:29,242
they find one person who is possessed, shouting, screaming,

54
00:05:30,899 --> 00:05:36,360
and a Sahaja Yogi who is really matured will say, “Now you get out of this place,

55
00:05:36,440 --> 00:05:38,929
you should not be here,” because that person

56
00:05:39,009 --> 00:05:41,759
will know that everybody will be troubled

57
00:05:41,839 --> 00:05:46,380
by this person, because this person has got a disease which will be contagious.

58
00:05:46,686 --> 00:05:52,019
All mental troubles are contagious which people do not know, like psychologists.

59
00:05:52,099 --> 00:05:54,460
They do not know that they are treating psychopaths.

60
00:05:54,540 --> 00:05:56,489
They themselves become psychopaths,

61
00:05:56,569 --> 00:05:59,902
because they have no way of protecting themselves.

62
00:06:00,564 --> 00:06:05,430
So first of all you must protect yourself and you find anybody like that,

63
00:06:05,510 --> 00:06:07,630
better not go near that person.

64
00:06:07,710 --> 00:06:12,800
At the most you can say, “Mother, look after this man,” if you have

65
00:06:12,880 --> 00:06:17,480
so much of feelings, but sympathy of this kind is very dangerous.

66
00:06:17,560 --> 00:06:21,289
I call it ‘symp’ means to share and ‘pathy’ means pathos.

67
00:06:21,369 --> 00:06:26,010
So you share the pathos of a madman and you get into troubles.

68
00:06:26,809 --> 00:06:31,890
So as good children I have to warn you that you should get more attached,

69
00:06:33,420 --> 00:06:41,149
more adhered to a person who is more evolved, more enlightened.

70
00:06:42,239 --> 00:06:46,639
Instead of that, people start feeling jealous and get ego-oriented

71
00:06:46,719 --> 00:06:51,529
and start fighting with a person who is much better off.

72
00:06:51,940 --> 00:06:57,730
Now Dr. Warren, as you know, has achieved it, a very great height in Sahaja Yoga,

73
00:07:01,019 --> 00:07:07,294
but in Australia, I found many people who were really jealous of him

74
00:07:07,374 --> 00:07:12,748
for nothing at all and they wanted to oust him, while they themselves were at

75
00:07:12,828 --> 00:07:17,704
the low ebb and they always wanted to go to people who are at a lower ebb.

76
00:07:17,784 --> 00:07:19,450
If you have to go higher,

77
00:07:19,530 --> 00:07:23,466
then you have to stick on to people who have gone little higher and

78
00:07:23,546 --> 00:07:27,049
not to go to such people who are at a lower ebb,

79
00:07:27,339 --> 00:07:30,570
while they can come up only by looking up.

80
00:07:31,386 --> 00:07:34,519
So you cannot bring them by going down to them.

81
00:07:34,599 --> 00:07:39,175
So those people who have got Realization for the first time, who have just touched

82
00:07:39,255 --> 00:07:41,319
it, should not suddenly start thinking:

83
00:07:41,399 --> 00:07:46,680
now they have become the great evolved people.

84
00:07:46,760 --> 00:07:55,549
They have to grow – grow like trees and acquire the knowledge of their powers.

85
00:07:55,629 --> 00:07:59,990
For example, if I entered into one room, that does not mean that I have gone to

86
00:08:00,070 --> 00:08:05,199
all the rooms, that does not mean that I know what is happening in other rooms.

87
00:08:05,279 --> 00:08:10,200
So for a person who has got Realization, has to be humble about it;

88
00:08:10,280 --> 00:08:14,946
that, I have to see more and I have to know more, I have to be better.

89
00:08:15,049 --> 00:08:18,079
This attitude helps a lot in their growth,

90
00:08:18,329 --> 00:08:25,703
and once you have achieved the higher state, which we call as Nirvikalpa, means

91
00:08:25,783 --> 00:08:36,450
doubtless awareness, after that you yourself can start with great enthusiasm,

92
00:08:36,979 --> 00:08:41,308
helping people, those who are much lower than you.

93
00:08:42,698 --> 00:08:46,109
This is one of the reasons many people who come to

94
00:08:46,189 --> 00:08:50,039
Sahaja Yoga go down and take lot of time to come up.

95
00:08:50,330 --> 00:08:52,039
Sahaja Yoga is becoming.

96
00:08:52,119 --> 00:08:56,052
It is not that you can make somebody a plastic Sahaja Yogi.

97
00:08:56,369 --> 00:08:59,169
You cannot give a certificate, “All right,

98
00:08:59,330 --> 00:09:05,530
now you are a realized soul.” It is you who has to certify yourself.

99
00:09:05,750 --> 00:09:10,669
It is you who has to grow up and it is you who has to master it.

100
00:09:11,580 --> 00:09:16,070
It is you who knows whether you have got it or not.

101
00:09:16,679 --> 00:09:21,640
So you have to have due respect for yourself and for others.

102
00:09:22,349 --> 00:09:26,820
The second problem arises that a person becomes bumptious

103
00:09:27,817 --> 00:09:31,417
and starts quarrelling with Sahaja Yogis, taking sides

104
00:09:31,497 --> 00:09:36,799
of people who are negative, people who are not yet anywhere

105
00:09:36,879 --> 00:09:40,479
– is also a common sight I have seen with many people.

106
00:09:41,190 --> 00:09:44,710
So one should see, “What changes have come in me,

107
00:09:45,359 --> 00:09:49,977
what transformation has taken place in me?” One can even write a

108
00:09:50,057 --> 00:09:53,159
diary to see, “Have I become more compassionate,

109
00:09:53,239 --> 00:09:58,270
have I become more tolerant, have I become much more nourishing?

110
00:09:58,413 --> 00:10:01,550
Can I share things with others?

111
00:10:01,630 --> 00:10:07,357
Do I enjoy the company of others and the company of Sahaja

112
00:10:07,437 --> 00:10:11,180
Yogis?” But that does not mean that you have to enjoy

113
00:10:11,260 --> 00:10:15,650
the company of the people who are not realized and not

114
00:10:15,730 --> 00:10:18,574
to enjoy the company of the people who are realized.

115
00:10:18,654 --> 00:10:23,820
In India we have very good saints and very realized souls,

116
00:10:23,900 --> 00:10:29,740
and their idea about human beings is very sad, because

117
00:10:29,820 --> 00:10:36,260
they think that human beings can never understand that when they have to grow up,

118
00:10:36,469 --> 00:10:38,869
they have to grow up with humility.

119
00:10:39,690 --> 00:10:44,410
Like a student has to learn from a professor, you have to learn from

120
00:10:44,490 --> 00:10:49,289
your Kundalini how to grow, how to become better by watching yourself.

121
00:10:50,830 --> 00:10:54,842
They think that unless and until the guru is very strict,

122
00:10:54,922 --> 00:10:58,539
actually, like the gurus you have in the market, they are not.

123
00:10:58,619 --> 00:11:00,630
They are very different type of people.

124
00:11:00,710 --> 00:11:03,549
They are terribly hard task masters.

125
00:11:03,629 --> 00:11:09,095
If you see, their methods are so horrifying that I shudder to send anyone to them.

126
00:11:09,254 --> 00:11:12,550
Once I had sent one gentleman, he had told Me,

127
00:11:12,630 --> 00:11:18,910
there was one guru called as Gagangad Maharaj, who is a real guru, and he is very

128
00:11:18,990 --> 00:11:23,872
well known, but he lives in the jungles and his legs are broken

129
00:11:23,952 --> 00:11:28,979
and hands are broken by human beings, and he is carried by a tiger.

130
00:11:30,286 --> 00:11:34,019
So he told Me, “Mother, if you, if anybody troubles you,

131
00:11:34,099 --> 00:11:35,393
if you are in difficulties with

132
00:11:35,473 --> 00:11:41,006
somebody who is very troublesome, you send him over to me.” So I said, “All right.”

133
00:11:41,115 --> 00:11:45,648
The one gentleman who was very torturesome, he used to ask questions

134
00:11:45,728 --> 00:11:49,849
after questions like mad and very troublesome fellow, very ego-oriented.

135
00:11:49,929 --> 00:11:54,137
So just I said, “All right, you go and see this guru.” Now this

136
00:11:54,217 --> 00:11:57,070
guru does not see people at all, so he felt very enamoured.

137
00:11:57,150 --> 00:12:00,279
His ego was pampered, “Oh God, the guru has called me,

138
00:12:00,359 --> 00:12:03,450
something great.” So he went to that guru.

139
00:12:03,530 --> 00:12:07,859
After a month he came back, and like there was a big passage,

140
00:12:08,729 --> 00:12:15,580
and his legs were on his neck, and they were ringing him, as if dangling towards Me.

141
00:12:15,660 --> 00:12:16,693
I looked at him.

142
00:12:16,773 --> 00:12:20,039
I could not bear it, and tears came into my eyes.

143
00:12:20,119 --> 00:12:23,270
I said, “What has happened to him?” He said, “Mother,

144
00:12:23,350 --> 00:12:28,550
I am sorry for what I did.” I said, “What happened?” He said, “You see,

145
00:12:28,630 --> 00:12:35,810
when I went there, I was rather bad because I told against you to the guru.” I said,

146
00:12:35,890 --> 00:12:37,570
“What did you tell against the guru?”

147
00:12:37,650 --> 00:12:40,570
He said: “I told that Mother is giving Realization to every Tom,

148
00:12:40,650 --> 00:12:44,482
Dick and Harry, and She should really first of all verify and

149
00:12:44,562 --> 00:12:49,450
then give Realization and this and that, and I was talking ill about you.” He said,

150
00:12:49,530 --> 00:12:52,539
“Yes, you are wiser than Mother, isn’t it?

151
00:12:52,619 --> 00:12:59,733
And then in the night the tiger came and threw me in a ‘khud’ and fell down,

152
00:12:59,813 --> 00:13:01,013
fourteen feet down.

153
00:13:01,093 --> 00:13:11,389
And then this guru lowered some bread after three days and asked that,

154
00:13:11,469 --> 00:13:22,309
“You can eat this food but stay there.” And I was lying there for five days.”

155
00:13:22,389 --> 00:13:30,289
And every day he (guru) used to lower the bread for him and he was there,

156
00:13:30,369 --> 00:13:34,270
all filled with filth and everything.

157
00:13:34,700 --> 00:13:38,900
After five, six days he sent three, four people to pick him up,

158
00:13:39,976 --> 00:13:46,670
and when he came up, he asked them to give him a bath and all that and a change.

159
00:13:46,750 --> 00:13:48,526
And then he told that,

160
00:13:48,606 --> 00:13:53,630
“You put these legs around your neck and go dangling to Mother.

161
00:13:53,710 --> 00:13:56,580
She is the one who will put you right, not me,

162
00:13:56,660 --> 00:13:58,979
and if you ever say a word against Mother,

163
00:13:59,059 --> 00:14:03,969
then I will break your legs in such a way that you will never be able to fix them.”

164
00:14:04,049 --> 00:14:08,839
Poor fellow, he was shattered, and he came to Me, “Mother,

165
00:14:08,919 --> 00:14:13,459
it was too much.” Of course, his legs were fixed.

166
00:14:13,539 --> 00:14:15,409
He is all right.

167
00:14:15,489 --> 00:14:19,169
He is a good fellow now, but that is what they do, because according to them,

168
00:14:19,249 --> 00:14:23,406
unless and until you take them to task, you cannot humble them down.

169
00:14:23,486 --> 00:14:24,819
Like another fellow.

170
00:14:24,899 --> 00:14:29,993
I sent him to another fellow who was a doctor and who used to really

171
00:14:30,073 --> 00:14:34,179
bother Me too much, but I just told him, go and see this particular guru.

172
00:14:34,259 --> 00:14:37,074
So when the doctor came back, he was thin like sticks.

173
00:14:37,154 --> 00:14:38,619
I said, what has happened?

174
00:14:38,699 --> 00:14:43,219
Didn’t he not give you food to eat? “No Mother, he gave me food all right,

175
00:14:43,299 --> 00:14:46,800
he was very affectionate.” But what happened, why did you lose so much weight?

176
00:14:46,880 --> 00:14:48,209
What has happened to you?

177
00:14:48,289 --> 00:14:51,110
You are looking so very thin.

178
00:14:51,190 --> 00:14:56,440
So he was staying about seven miles, one had to walk up, and every day he

179
00:14:56,520 --> 00:15:01,809
had to carry two buckets of water to clean one dilapidated temple there.

180
00:15:02,823 --> 00:15:06,289
Every day he was supposed to take that and clean it.

181
00:15:06,369 --> 00:15:10,700
So I asked this guru, “What do you mean by torturing him like this, taking these

182
00:15:10,780 --> 00:15:15,300
two buckets to clean the thing?” He said, “For a donkey you must give donkey’s work.

183
00:15:15,380 --> 00:15:19,570
I am not a Mother to look after these ego-oriented people.

184
00:15:19,650 --> 00:15:23,516
It is better that he is trash now, he will be better off.”

185
00:15:23,659 --> 00:15:27,899
So this is what, the way they think people can be taught and

186
00:15:27,979 --> 00:15:32,120
they are to learn their lessons of spirituality in this way.

187
00:15:32,200 --> 00:15:37,950
Even when you go to them, they will test you in so many ways that you absolutely get

188
00:15:39,593 --> 00:15:45,059
fed up and you leave them and they are very happy that you have left them forever.

189
00:15:45,139 --> 00:15:47,581
They are never anxious that you should be close to

190
00:15:47,661 --> 00:15:50,399
them because it is a thankless job, otherwise if

191
00:15:50,479 --> 00:15:53,020
you see, if you do not take any money,

192
00:15:53,100 --> 00:15:56,859
you are never rewarded, people try to always boss over you.

193
00:15:56,939 --> 00:16:00,860
So they think that: it is better first to put them right,

194
00:16:00,940 --> 00:16:05,179
let them learn that you have to go hard way to be the Spirit.

195
00:16:06,220 --> 00:16:08,820
But Sahaja Yoga today is not like that.

196
00:16:09,597 --> 00:16:13,397
As a Mother I thought, let these children who are already

197
00:16:13,477 --> 00:16:16,286
under pressure and tension receive their Realization.

198
00:16:16,366 --> 00:16:18,473
Let them have their Realization.

199
00:16:18,553 --> 00:16:23,419
Let them have their light again and let them see what is wrong with them.

200
00:16:23,499 --> 00:16:27,640
Then they start seeing their ego, they start seeing their superego,

201
00:16:27,720 --> 00:16:31,088
they start seeing their conditionings, they start seeing

202
00:16:31,168 --> 00:16:35,013
their problems and gradually when they see it, they can cleanse it,

203
00:16:35,093 --> 00:16:38,529
if you tell them how to cleanse it and they work it out.

204
00:16:38,609 --> 00:16:44,479
So after Realization, it is very important how you look after yourself.

205
00:16:44,559 --> 00:16:48,310
You may be a king, you may be anything, makes no difference.

206
00:16:48,390 --> 00:16:53,270
In the realm of God, the one who is an evolved soul is respected.

207
00:16:53,640 --> 00:17:00,200
Not the person who just is a big man or something, a big politician, has no place.

208
00:17:00,830 --> 00:17:03,309
Only thing is who is more evolved.

209
00:17:04,098 --> 00:17:09,969
Even a simple person on the street can come to Sahaja Yoga and can rise very high,

210
00:17:10,260 --> 00:17:12,676
and a person who comes in a big car

211
00:17:12,756 --> 00:17:18,567
and a big way and tries to all the time impress upon Me the

212
00:17:18,647 --> 00:17:22,647
greatness of his worldly treasures, does not reach anywhere.

213
00:17:23,823 --> 00:17:28,089
So in the eyes of God, it is not important what you are in life,

214
00:17:28,178 --> 00:17:32,711
what your ego tells you, what you think of yourself, but it is God’s

215
00:17:32,791 --> 00:17:36,711
judgment that He sees how far you are in Realization,

216
00:17:37,154 --> 00:17:42,420
and in Realization you have to judge yourself through your vibratory awareness.

217
00:17:42,760 --> 00:17:48,828
When this awareness stations down properly and you really become absolutely

218
00:17:48,908 --> 00:17:55,949
endowed with it, the joy of Sahaja Yoga starts trickling in your existence.

219
00:17:56,029 --> 00:17:57,489
People can see you.

220
00:17:57,569 --> 00:18:04,399
Those who never laughed, started laughing aloud, feeling the joy of life.

221
00:18:04,479 --> 00:18:08,199
The whole drama becomes sometimes a comedy,

222
00:18:08,279 --> 00:18:12,430
sometimes a tragedy and you start seeing the whole drama

223
00:18:12,510 --> 00:18:16,599
as a witness, and when this happens, then a person really,

224
00:18:16,770 --> 00:18:20,589
really enjoys the beauty of their Spirit.

225
00:18:20,920 --> 00:18:23,989
But those who think that they are great and

226
00:18:24,069 --> 00:18:26,639
they have read this book and they have been to

227
00:18:26,719 --> 00:18:29,310
this guru or they have done this great job,

228
00:18:29,390 --> 00:18:32,520
they must know that it is not counted at all.

229
00:18:32,930 --> 00:18:38,931
It is how you are within yourself, where are your vibrations and what

230
00:18:39,011 --> 00:18:43,959
are the chakras you have opened out, how much large you have grown.

231
00:18:44,130 --> 00:18:47,560
That is how a person is known by his evolution.

232
00:18:47,969 --> 00:18:49,989
You are all seekers of ages.

233
00:18:50,069 --> 00:18:52,069
You are not a seeker of today.

234
00:18:52,520 --> 00:18:57,882
You have been seeking in previous lives and many lives before and so you are

235
00:18:57,962 --> 00:19:02,780
here today to seek the truth, and the truth is to be faced as the truth is.

236
00:19:02,860 --> 00:19:05,737
You cannot force the truth to be like you want to be.

237
00:19:05,817 --> 00:19:10,417
Like some people say, “But Mother, I still like this.” Then go ahead.

238
00:19:10,553 --> 00:19:11,619
I do not say no.

239
00:19:11,699 --> 00:19:13,180
I never say no to anything.

240
00:19:13,260 --> 00:19:16,020
I said, “Go ahead” and they then learn a lesson.

241
00:19:16,100 --> 00:19:20,562
Like one day I will tell you about Dr. Warren himself, a very interesting story.

242
00:19:20,642 --> 00:19:23,690
It happened only few days back when we were in Singapore.

243
00:19:23,770 --> 00:19:26,770
I just tried some tricks and make them learn.

244
00:19:26,850 --> 00:19:29,924
Like there is another nice lady, very nice lady,

245
00:19:30,004 --> 00:19:33,656
who is very evolved and all that, and she got

246
00:19:33,736 --> 00:19:34,936
after him that,

247
00:19:35,016 --> 00:19:38,414
“We must go now to Kuala Lumpur,” because she lives in Kuala Lumpur and she was

248
00:19:38,494 --> 00:19:40,500
worried about the meetings and this and that,

249
00:19:40,580 --> 00:19:42,702
and I had told them that I am going out and I will

250
00:19:42,782 --> 00:19:44,540
be coming back and we will all go together

251
00:19:44,620 --> 00:19:46,132
because there is a shuttle service all the time.

252
00:19:46,212 --> 00:19:50,678
And I said, we will go by the evening plane, but they wanted, she wanted to

253
00:19:50,758 --> 00:19:54,550
go two hours earlier, and she was after him that, “You better come along.

254
00:19:54,630 --> 00:19:59,009
Mother has a ticket and she will come along.” And there were other people with Me,

255
00:19:59,089 --> 00:20:04,310
so these went just to organize everything, two hours earlier, by the plane.

256
00:20:04,390 --> 00:20:09,460
When they went there, they reached all right, two hours,

257
00:20:09,540 --> 00:20:17,506
but when I arrived at the hall, what I find that they were getting down from their

258
00:20:17,586 --> 00:20:22,283
car – means they arrived even later than I had arrived, and I thought

259
00:20:22,363 --> 00:20:25,539
they will be now very much embarrassed to see Me getting down with them.

260
00:20:25,619 --> 00:20:27,019
So I asked the driver, I said,

261
00:20:27,099 --> 00:20:33,300
“Let us go ahead till they come out of the car,” and I asked them what had happened.

262
00:20:33,380 --> 00:20:37,656
They said that, “We got down all right, but on the way there was a big jam,

263
00:20:37,736 --> 00:20:43,480
and we did not know how to go, so we thought, better take another road.

264
00:20:43,560 --> 00:20:48,979
So we came out from the pavement on the sides, and when we came out,

265
00:20:50,339 --> 00:20:56,981
there was all, we found that this was all filled with mud.” So the car

266
00:20:57,061 --> 00:21:01,094
got stuck in the mud and they had to pull it out and all sorts of things

267
00:21:01,174 --> 00:21:05,554
had to be done, and they reached little later than when I had arrived.

268
00:21:05,634 --> 00:21:07,900
Then she realized, she said, “Yes,

269
00:21:07,980 --> 00:21:11,472
that Warren was telling me all the time that you should not do something

270
00:21:11,552 --> 00:21:14,816
that Mother has said, we should go with Her because She looks after everything,

271
00:21:14,896 --> 00:21:16,090
so why should we worry?”

272
00:21:16,170 --> 00:21:20,040
So like that, you see, little, little incidents start occurring in your

273
00:21:20,120 --> 00:21:24,680
life and you start understanding that we are unnecessarily worried.

274
00:21:24,849 --> 00:21:27,359
Like sometimes, as our habits are,

275
00:21:27,569 --> 00:21:33,319
we want to go to the airport even before the aeroplane is fitted there.

276
00:21:33,399 --> 00:21:35,420
I mean, we are so futuristic,

277
00:21:35,500 --> 00:21:40,280
and there are people always with Me who are of that type and they get after My

278
00:21:40,360 --> 00:21:43,279
life saying, “Mother, you should get ready now, we have to go,

279
00:21:43,359 --> 00:21:45,399
we have to go,” and they become so quite wobbly.

280
00:21:45,479 --> 00:21:48,139
I said, “All right, to put you at rest, I will come,

281
00:21:48,219 --> 00:21:50,431
but there is nothing going to happen, we are just in

282
00:21:50,511 --> 00:21:54,229
time, don’t you worry.” So we reach the airport and there they say,

283
00:21:54,309 --> 00:21:56,887
suddenly the plane is delayed by two hours.

284
00:21:56,967 --> 00:21:58,700
So they cannot understand,

285
00:21:58,780 --> 00:22:01,409
the plane was not delayed and why the plane is delayed now.

286
00:22:01,489 --> 00:22:03,289
Now I said, “Now, settle down.

287
00:22:03,369 --> 00:22:09,119
Fix your left Nabhi, fix your wobbly nature and let us work it out at the airport.”

288
00:22:09,333 --> 00:22:10,690
This is what it is.

289
00:22:10,770 --> 00:22:15,743
One has to slowly and steadily understand that the God who

290
00:22:15,823 --> 00:22:19,810
has created this great universe is the one looking after.

291
00:22:20,406 --> 00:22:22,939
He is the one who is looking after us.

292
00:22:23,150 --> 00:22:24,859
His angels are around us.

293
00:22:25,006 --> 00:22:29,339
They all look after all the realized souls who are on this earth.

294
00:22:29,419 --> 00:22:35,639
All the beautiful Ritambhara Pragnya,

295
00:22:35,719 --> 00:22:46,599
that is the knowledge of the enlightened mind about the seasons of beauty.

296
00:22:49,310 --> 00:22:52,910
They start enjoying it, and when it happens to you,

297
00:22:53,959 --> 00:22:56,959
even it happens to you, you just do not worry

298
00:22:57,259 --> 00:23:01,459
because you understand that everything is laid bare before you,

299
00:23:01,539 --> 00:23:04,109
and it has happened with so many people,

300
00:23:04,189 --> 00:23:07,480
but there could be another person who may not accept and say,

301
00:23:07,560 --> 00:23:09,167
“No, no, no, no, no, no, we must be

302
00:23:09,247 --> 00:23:11,947
very careful, we must do this and this” and start worrying,

303
00:23:12,027 --> 00:23:13,680
the same way they have been worrying.

304
00:23:13,760 --> 00:23:17,301
Actually some people get upset even if you mention them

305
00:23:17,381 --> 00:23:19,879
that you have to go to the airport, I have seen that,

306
00:23:19,959 --> 00:23:23,159
and then they find that they are losing their passports,

307
00:23:23,239 --> 00:23:26,150
they are losing this and that, getting so wobbly.

308
00:23:26,230 --> 00:23:29,417
In Sahaja Yoga, first of all, you must steady yourself.

309
00:23:29,497 --> 00:23:31,820
You must try to steady yourself.

310
00:23:31,900 --> 00:23:34,510
Put your left Nabhi as they say,

311
00:23:34,680 --> 00:23:39,680
here is the left Nabhi – This one is to be put at ease.

312
00:23:39,780 --> 00:23:45,530
Is very important, because if it is not at ease, then also there is a

313
00:23:45,610 --> 00:23:51,010
possibility of you heading for some sort of a very serious disease like leukemia.

314
00:23:51,140 --> 00:23:57,444
As I told you the other day, that with the overactivity of this centre, on the

315
00:23:57,524 --> 00:24:03,539
left hand side, people might develop leukemia because your spleen becomes hectic.

316
00:24:03,619 --> 00:24:07,604
It becomes very nervous and it becomes crazy actually,

317
00:24:07,684 --> 00:24:12,680
because you are doing ten things at the same time and you are yourself crazy.

318
00:24:12,760 --> 00:24:14,790
So this becomes crazy,

319
00:24:14,870 --> 00:24:20,070
it starts producing malignant cells and you develop a disease called leukemia.

320
00:24:21,329 --> 00:24:25,630
So first of all you must put yourself to a peaceful life.

321
00:24:26,660 --> 00:24:28,060
Now how do you do it?

322
00:24:28,209 --> 00:24:32,810
First of all believe that you are not going to miss anything in life.

323
00:24:32,890 --> 00:24:37,090
Even if you miss, supposing you think that you have to miss it.

324
00:24:37,359 --> 00:24:45,150
Like once at the airport we reached and the plane was late for five hours in Bombay,

325
00:24:45,820 --> 00:24:48,420
and in Bombay people know Me very well.

326
00:24:48,500 --> 00:24:51,220
They came to know that I am at the airport.

327
00:24:51,300 --> 00:24:56,211
Right from pilots to the loaders, everybody came there to get Realization

328
00:24:56,291 --> 00:25:00,557
and about five hundred of them came down and they got their Realization.

329
00:25:00,637 --> 00:25:05,170
So My sitting there was important, My doing that work was important,

330
00:25:05,250 --> 00:25:08,229
so the plane was late and everybody enjoyed it.

331
00:25:08,309 --> 00:25:13,609
So to get upset about what you have thought that you are going to do next moment,

332
00:25:13,689 --> 00:25:15,289
and when you do not

333
00:25:15,369 --> 00:25:20,691
do it, then you feel, “Oh God,” the whole joy is finished,

334
00:25:20,771 --> 00:25:23,390
because people live with futuristic ideas.

335
00:25:23,470 --> 00:25:27,485
The whole future they built-in beforehand and they expect that future

336
00:25:27,565 --> 00:25:31,069
to happen and when that future does not happen they become miserable.

337
00:25:31,149 --> 00:25:35,489
Actually in Sahaja Yoga you are in the present, you are never in the future.

338
00:25:35,569 --> 00:25:41,599
Absolutely silent and absolutely peaceful with yourself, you are in the present.

339
00:25:41,679 --> 00:25:43,904
You are dealing with the present moment.

340
00:25:43,984 --> 00:25:47,050
So the present moment is the reality while the

341
00:25:47,130 --> 00:25:50,159
future does not exist and the past is finished.

342
00:25:50,239 --> 00:25:56,059
So where you are, you are in the present, where you are enjoying the

343
00:25:56,139 --> 00:25:59,249
dynamism of the present, and this is what I have found with Sahaja

344
00:25:59,329 --> 00:26:02,549
Yogis is that when first they get their Realization,

345
00:26:03,107 --> 00:26:08,640
they either go to the future or to the past according to what they have been doing.

346
00:26:08,969 --> 00:26:14,920
Now the people who are, who have been indulging into the left side also can be

347
00:26:15,000 --> 00:26:19,920
very much harmful themselves because they also start living with their past.

348
00:26:20,000 --> 00:26:22,769
Most of them I have seen, they will come to Me,

349
00:26:22,849 --> 00:26:25,341
“Mother, my father is not all right, my

350
00:26:25,421 --> 00:26:28,680
mother is not all right, my grandfather is not all right,

351
00:26:28,760 --> 00:26:30,570
my grandmother is not all right.”

352
00:26:30,650 --> 00:26:33,543
The attention immediately goes to the whole,

353
00:26:34,630 --> 00:26:37,543
whole lineage, to whole progeny, “My son is

354
00:26:37,623 --> 00:26:42,423
like that, my grandson is like that,” but if you get all right yourself,

355
00:26:42,750 --> 00:26:44,580
you are the centre.

356
00:26:44,660 --> 00:26:47,980
You are the centre of the whole core and once you are all

357
00:26:48,060 --> 00:26:50,803
right you can put everyone all right, but what happens

358
00:26:50,883 --> 00:26:54,019
that suddenly the attention shifts, you see, this is the habit;

359
00:26:54,099 --> 00:26:57,530
to shift the attention for yourself to others.

360
00:26:57,610 --> 00:27:00,284
Then the shifting starts about other Sahaja Yogis:

361
00:27:00,364 --> 00:27:02,885
“That Sahaja Yogi is like that and this Sahaja Yogi

362
00:27:02,965 --> 00:27:05,806
is like that, and that Sahaja Yogi did this and that

363
00:27:05,886 --> 00:27:08,649
Sahaja Yogi did this.” Like some people who are

364
00:27:08,729 --> 00:27:12,300
absolutely such that we cannot call them Sahaja Yogis but they come,

365
00:27:12,380 --> 00:27:14,150
they go, they are still going on

366
00:27:14,230 --> 00:27:15,680
and then people see them and they say,

367
00:27:15,760 --> 00:27:18,480
“If this is the Sahaja Yogi, I do not want to be a Sahaja Yogi.”

368
00:27:18,560 --> 00:27:24,569
It is like this, the shifting of the mind starts and people try not to be there,

369
00:27:25,250 --> 00:27:29,229
but you must position yourself on your Spirit.

370
00:27:29,309 --> 00:27:31,470
You must know that you have become the Spirit.

371
00:27:31,550 --> 00:27:37,965
Position yourself is the point and then once you have grown into it, then you do not

372
00:27:38,045 --> 00:27:43,119
relate yourself in this way, that, “My father, my mother.” This ‘my’ finishes off.

373
00:27:43,199 --> 00:27:46,275
Then you think, “Yes, my father is here,

374
00:27:46,355 --> 00:27:49,881
who is a person who should come to Sahaja Yoga.” You go up to a

375
00:27:49,961 --> 00:27:51,578
point, tell him, “All right, if you can come,

376
00:27:51,658 --> 00:27:54,440
well and good.” If he does not come, you are not bothered.

377
00:27:54,520 --> 00:27:57,629
You develop your relationship with the Father,

378
00:27:57,709 --> 00:28:01,737
God Almighty and with the Mother who has given you Realization.

379
00:28:02,086 --> 00:28:03,619
This is very important.

380
00:28:03,699 --> 00:28:05,699
Then secondly it starts like this.

381
00:28:05,779 --> 00:28:10,830
Like, of course, there have been great saints in our country,

382
00:28:10,910 --> 00:28:18,516
like we can say that we had Sai Nath, he was a realized soul, a great person and his

383
00:28:18,596 --> 00:28:22,359
disciples would come to Me and they will say, “All right, Mother,

384
00:28:22,439 --> 00:28:27,439
you have given us Realization, thank you very much, but Sai Nath, you see, we have

385
00:28:27,519 --> 00:28:32,899
Sai Nath’s photograph, we worship Sai Nath.” Now this is another style,

386
00:28:32,979 --> 00:28:37,676
is that now Christ is not here, so when Krishna came, they said, “Oh, we will

387
00:28:37,756 --> 00:28:42,329
talk about Dattatreya, not about Krishna.” When Rama came, they said,

388
00:28:42,409 --> 00:28:47,300
“We will talk about somebody who came before Him.” Never when they were there.

389
00:28:47,380 --> 00:28:53,473
When Abraham came or Moses came, so they said, “Let us talk about somebody

390
00:28:53,553 --> 00:28:58,065
who came before.” When that happened, then when Christ came, they said, “Let

391
00:28:58,145 --> 00:29:02,499
us talk about Moses.” And now I have come, I have given you Realization,

392
00:29:02,579 --> 00:29:07,096
then you would like to learn everything from Christ, who is no more there.

393
00:29:07,703 --> 00:29:09,569
He is not going to tell you.

394
00:29:10,563 --> 00:29:11,829
I have to tell you.

395
00:29:11,909 --> 00:29:14,810
That does not mean you are disrespectful to Christ.

396
00:29:14,890 --> 00:29:20,050
Christ is as much there as Myself, but I have to tell you, not Christ.

397
00:29:20,139 --> 00:29:24,739
That is not His responsibility at this time, it is My responsibility,

398
00:29:24,819 --> 00:29:28,426
and so one must understand, who has given you the Realization?

399
00:29:28,506 --> 00:29:33,439
And that is why Christ has said that anything against Me will be forgiven,

400
00:29:33,519 --> 00:29:36,441
but nothing against the Holy Ghost, because the Holy Ghost

401
00:29:36,521 --> 00:29:39,644
will give you the Realization, and after taking the Realization also,

402
00:29:39,724 --> 00:29:43,560
if you try to put yourself backwards, then you cannot go further.

403
00:29:43,640 --> 00:29:47,973
So one has to understand, that who has given you the Realization?

404
00:29:49,961 --> 00:29:53,094
The same thing happens about gurus, this, that.

405
00:29:53,174 --> 00:29:56,729
People are sucked back, but what have they given you, is the point.

406
00:29:56,809 --> 00:29:58,650
You should know what have they given you.

407
00:29:58,730 --> 00:30:00,779
Have they given you something substantial?

408
00:30:00,859 --> 00:30:01,820
They have not.

409
00:30:01,900 --> 00:30:07,209
Then why are you sticking onto that which is not going to give you what you want?

410
00:30:07,289 --> 00:30:09,659
They are not going to answer your questions.

411
00:30:09,739 --> 00:30:12,859
They are not going to tell you anything about it.

412
00:30:12,939 --> 00:30:15,540
So why not ask a person who can speak,

413
00:30:16,380 --> 00:30:20,289
who can tell you, who can explain, who is in present?

414
00:30:21,026 --> 00:30:23,359
And this is another human weakness,

415
00:30:23,439 --> 00:30:27,438
that they do not want to live in the present, but some people

416
00:30:27,518 --> 00:30:30,622
will say, “No, the Messiah is going to come after,

417
00:30:30,702 --> 00:30:33,876
say, two thousand years.” Then you won’t be there.

418
00:30:33,956 --> 00:30:38,289
Today I am here, so better have your Realization, learn about it.

419
00:30:38,369 --> 00:30:41,359
When He comes afterwards, another one, then it is all right,

420
00:30:41,439 --> 00:30:44,372
but that time you are not going to be there.

421
00:30:44,556 --> 00:30:48,489
So the importance of present, Sahaja Yogis must understand.

422
00:30:48,610 --> 00:30:50,810
At present what is the situation?

423
00:30:51,140 --> 00:30:52,089
Where am I?

424
00:30:52,169 --> 00:30:53,300
What have I done?

425
00:30:53,380 --> 00:30:56,290
I have to understand each and everything at present.

426
00:30:56,370 --> 00:30:58,170
This is the important time.

427
00:30:58,339 --> 00:31:04,960
I am not going to lose any time thinking about the past or about the future.

428
00:31:05,040 --> 00:31:07,270
At this time what is my problem is?

429
00:31:07,350 --> 00:31:09,119
And then the growth starts.

430
00:31:09,199 --> 00:31:14,550
All living things, whatever it is, works on present, never on the past.

431
00:31:14,880 --> 00:31:19,519
Say, as I told you yesterday, a root, when it starts sprouting,

432
00:31:19,599 --> 00:31:23,914
there is a little, small, little cell at the end of the root.

433
00:31:24,520 --> 00:31:27,960
It just sees what is the situation at that time is.

434
00:31:28,040 --> 00:31:33,939
All right, at this time it is a hard soil, it waits.

435
00:31:35,130 --> 00:31:39,130
As soon as the soil becomes little better, it starts moving.

436
00:31:39,210 --> 00:31:40,659
Then it creates a boulder.

437
00:31:40,739 --> 00:31:42,980
All right, the boulder is there, let us go round.

438
00:31:43,060 --> 00:31:44,779
At the present you have to achieve it.

439
00:31:44,859 --> 00:31:49,539
You can only achieve at the present, never in the future and never in the past.

440
00:31:49,619 --> 00:31:51,435
So this is another thing.

441
00:31:51,515 --> 00:31:55,100
The Sahaja Yogis who are realized souls must understand that

442
00:31:55,180 --> 00:31:59,010
they have to move with the present and not with the past.

443
00:31:59,090 --> 00:32:03,956
I had to go on fighting with people, telling them: now be in the present.

444
00:32:04,149 --> 00:32:09,349
Now the knowledge of Kundalini was never told so clearly, as it is said today.

445
00:32:09,810 --> 00:32:11,010
Now they will say,

446
00:32:11,090 --> 00:32:15,413
but people used to get Realization after so much of cleansing and this.

447
00:32:15,493 --> 00:32:17,693
That was thousands of years back.

448
00:32:20,206 --> 00:32:21,939
Now we can go to the moon.

449
00:32:23,169 --> 00:32:25,569
How many people went to moon before?

450
00:32:25,649 --> 00:32:30,149
So do we say “No, but they used to, never used to go to the moon,

451
00:32:30,229 --> 00:32:33,729
so how can we go?” It is just like that.

452
00:32:33,809 --> 00:32:38,249
If something has worked out like this, that it is a jet Kundalini now,

453
00:32:38,329 --> 00:32:41,989
and you can go to your Spirit, you can become your Spirit.

454
00:32:42,069 --> 00:32:44,119
Why not take the advantage of that?

455
00:32:44,199 --> 00:32:47,189
It is because the mind is not yet tuned.

456
00:32:48,300 --> 00:32:51,839
The mind has not understood the importance of time,

457
00:32:52,290 --> 00:32:56,632
and this time, this present time, is the most

458
00:32:56,712 --> 00:32:59,220
important time in the whole history of evolution,

459
00:32:59,300 --> 00:33:01,609
I can tell you, which you will realize very soon.

460
00:33:01,689 --> 00:33:06,587
It is the most important time, but people do not realize it, and for them, what

