866
00:56:36,307 --> 00:56:41,840
Whatever you have done or whatever has been there, forget it, forget it, forget it.

867
00:56:41,920 --> 00:56:43,649
You are not to feel guilty at all.

868
00:56:43,729 --> 00:56:46,080
At this moment you are in the present.

869
00:56:46,160 --> 00:56:48,809
