Here you have to say or ask a question to Me, calling Me Mother, if it is easier,

904
00:59:00,040 --> 00:59:06,340
“Mother, am I the Spirit?” Ask the question, “Mother, am I the Spirit?”

905
00:59:28,483 --> 00:59:32,149
If you are wearing any Malas or anything from any guru,

906
00:59:32,229 --> 00:59:36,050
