910
00:59:49,209 --> 00:59:55,919
We have to be ourselves to begin with and then only we belong to the Kingdom of God.

911
00:59:57,550 --> 01:00:04,100
Now just say, “Mother, am I the Spirit?” Ask thrice.

912
01:00:15,439 --> 01:00:24,139
Now put this right hand down on the stomach, on the left hand side and press it.

913
01:00:24,219 --> 01:00:29,352
This is the centre of the Primordial Master and as the Spirit is your master,

914
01:00:32,260 --> 01:00:33,929
