915
01:00:35,530 --> 01:00:41,139
So you have to say, “Mother, I am my own master.” You have to say that ten times.

916
01:01:09,699 --> 01:01:13,610
After saying that, you put this hand little lower,

917
01:01:13,690 --> 01:01:17,179
at the lower side of your stomach, on the left hand side.

918
01:01:17,259 --> 01:01:21,299
We are working the left hand side only.

919
01:01:21,379 --> 01:01:24,909
Now at this point you have to say, “Mother,

920
01:01:25,189 --> 01:01:29,790
