921
01:01:30,324 --> 01:01:49,389
Mother, make me the Divine technique.” Six times.

922
01:01:49,469 --> 01:01:52,050
Good.

923
01:01:55,189 --> 01:01:58,300
Now you again put your hand on your heart.

924
01:02:00,770 --> 01:02:04,889
Now with full assertion, without any guilt,

925
01:02:05,219 --> 01:02:09,929
