926
01:02:10,539 --> 01:02:14,139
“Mother, I am the Spirit,” because you are the Spirit,

927
01:02:14,219 --> 01:02:16,290
you are the Spirit, you are the Spirit.

928
01:02:16,370 --> 01:02:33,170
So you have to say, “Mother, I am the Spirit.”

929
01:02:33,250 --> 01:02:37,450
Now you put your right hand, raise it on the base of your neck,

930
01:02:56,049 --> 01:02:59,049
