931
01:03:00,320 --> 01:03:08,939
At this point you have to say, sixteen times, “Mother, I am not guilty.”

932
01:03:49,840 --> 01:03:55,590
Now raise this right hand on your forehead across.

933
01:03:56,609 --> 01:03:59,209
At this point you have to say, “Mother,

934
01:03:59,330 --> 01:04:07,310
